<span style="font-weight: bold;"><br>
The back story:&nbsp; </span>Arimaa was invented at about the same
time Boardspace was started, and I've been aware of Arimaa from the
beginning.&nbsp; Originally, Arimaa seemed to be mainly a robot
programming challenge, and therefore not a high priority for
Boardspace.&nbsp;&nbsp; The interesting thing, following the ongoing
ebb and flow of programs verses humans on Arimaa.com, was that there
was real interest in the game from human players, not just among
programmers.&nbsp; <br>
